In the example below we will use the `inferno` colormap to make a plot of fake population
numbers of towns on the island of St. Lucia. To do this, we'll use the file

[https://su-ist356-m003-fall-2025.github.io/course-home/assets/stlucia.geojson](../assets/stlucia.geojson)

This is a GeoJSON file that gives the borders of towns and villages in St. Lucia:

::: {#383aa1b2 .cell execution_count=9}
